WITH cte AS(
  SELECT * FROM (
    SELECT 
      *,
      SUM(amount) OVER(PARTITION BY user_id ORDER BY trx_date) AS rn_total
    FROM transactions
  )
  WHERE rn_total < 0
), cte_2 AS(
  SELECT 
    *,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY user_id ORDER BY trx_date) AS rnk
  FROM cte
)
SELECT * FROM cte_2
WHERE rnk = 1;

WITH cte_1 AS (
  SELECT 
    account_id,
    SUM(amount)
  FROM transactions
  WHERE date >= (
    SELECT MAX(date) - INTERVAL '30 DAYS' FROM transactions
  )
  GROUP BY account_id
  HAVING SUM(amount) >= 1000
), cte_2 AS(
  SELECT * FROM cte_1
  INNER JOIN user_balance ub ON cte_1.account_id = ub.id
)
SELECT
  c.user_id,
  u.name,
  c.account_id,
  c.balance - c.sum AS r_balance
FROM cte_2 c
INNER JOIN users u ON c.user_id = u.id
WHERE (c.balance - c.sum) >= 0

    SUM(amount)
  FROM transactions
  WHERE date >= (
    SELECT MAX(date) - INTERVAL '30 DAYS' FROM transactions
  )
  GROUP BY account_id
  HAVING SUM(amount) >= 1000
), cte_2 AS(
  SELECT * FROM cte_1
  INNER JOIN user_balance ub ON cte_1.account_id = ub.id
)
SELECT
  c.user_id,
  u.name,
  c.account_id,
  c.balance - c.sum AS r_balance
FROM cte_2 c
INNER JOIN users u ON c.user_id = u.id
WHERE (c.balance - c.sum) >= 0

SELECT 
    visited_on,
    ROUND(SUM(amount) OVER(ORDER BY visited_on ROWS BETWEEN 6 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW), 2) AS amount,
    ROUND(AVG(amount) OVER(ORDER BY visited_on ROWS BETWEEN 6 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW), 2) AS average_amount 
FROM (
    SELECT visited_on, SUM(amount) AS amount FROM Customer GROUP BY visited_on
)
ORDER BY visited_on
OFFSET 6

# Set yaratish usullari
s = {1, 2, 3, 3, 2}
s = set([1, 2, 2, 3])
print(s)

# Tartibi yo‚Äòq (index ishlamaydi)
s = {10, 20, 30}
# s[0] 

# Setni ichiga o'zgarmas qiymatlar bo'ladi
{1, "a", (1, 2)}  # ‚úì 
{1, [2, 3]}       # ‚úï

# Element qo‚Äòshish
s = {1, 2, 3}
s.add(4)
print(s)

# Element o‚Äòchirish
s.remove(2)     # yo‚Äòq bo‚Äòlsa xato beradi
s.discard(10)   # yo‚Äòq bo‚Äòlsa xato bermaydi

# Update
b = {2, 3, 4, 4}
a = {3, 55 ,6, 6}
b.update(a)

# Loop
s = {10, 20, 30}
for x in s:
    print(x)

# Union
a = {1, 2, 3}
b = {3, 4, 5}
print(a | b)
# yoki
print(a.union(b))

# Intersection
print(a & b)
# yoki
print(a.intersection(b))

# Difference
print(a - b)

text.text:
# Dictionary yaratish
student = {
    "name": "Ali",
    "age": 20,
    "score": 85
}

# dict 
student = dict(name="Ali", age=20, score=85)

## Dictionary elementlariga murojaat
# Key orqali
print(student["name"])

# get() ‚Äî xavfsiz usul
print(student.get("phone"))
print(student.get("phone", "yo‚Äòq"))

# Qiymat qo‚Äòshish va o‚Äòzgartirish
student["age"] = 21
student["phone"] = "998901234567"

# Update
d1 = {"a": 10, "b": 20, "c": 30}
d2 = {"b": 5, "c": 15, "d": 40}
d1.update(d2)

# O‚Äòchirish
del student["score"]
student.pop("age")
student.clear()

# Loop
for key in student:
    print(key)

for value in student.values():
    print(value)

for k, v in student.items():
    print(k, v)
